{"tid":2326192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"落力跳舞變小豬！39歲汪東城被網民批老土似「狗射尿」","createTime":"2020-12-15T06:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:34:24.000Z","uid":318316,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c0023441d28df374fc82e5a53705687696967bc9","tid":2326192,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OsVeb7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OsVeb7.gif&h=04cb4dab&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tP7BH6q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtP7BH6q.gif&h=980c2e18&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJbfed8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJbfed8.gif&h=a95ef7b9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJsib1T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJsib1T.gif&h=38a2cb74&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeAcgwV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeAcgwV.gif&h=41a875f1&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201213/bkn-20201213173331694-1213_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201213%2Fbkn-20201213173331694-1213_00862_001.html&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=b2259512\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201213/bkn-20201213173331694-1213_00862_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n台灣藝人汪東城參與大陸綜藝節目《追光吧！哥哥》，他跳唱舊作《我應該去愛你》，還加插了《A Good Night》舞步，表現相當落力，用雙手撐起身再提腿，又貼近地板單膝跪地，半邊身狂扭動踢腿，不過動作欠利落，且可能太出力關係，臉容有點扭曲，但觀眾依然興奮大聲尖叫，最後他瞓在地上再使出一招拱橋作完結。內地演員杜淳笑說：「動作讓我做會很油膩。」任觀察員的內地女星鄭爽就咬手指又掩嘴大笑。"},{"pid":"4e5f5e5eee85422bb1205565ee47e9a0aeccaa93","tid":2326192,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"型到盡頭便是柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/as